## MANAJEMEN RISIKO

### Kategori Risiko Utama

#### Technical Risks

**Smart Contract Vulnerabilities (High Risk)**
- **Description**: Potential bugs dalam smart contracts yang dapat menyebabkan financial losses
- **Impact**: Critical - Potensi kehilangan dana investor, reputational damage
- **Mitigation Strategies**:
  - Multiple independent security audits dari reputable firms
  - Extensive unit dan integration testing dengan edge case coverage
  - Formal verification untuk critical contract functions
  - Bug bounty program post-launch dengan substantial rewards
  - Emergency pause mechanisms dalam all financial contracts

**Blockchain Scalability Limitations (High Risk)**
- **Description**: DPOS consensus mungkin tidak dapat handle high transaction volumes
- **Impact**: High - Platform performance degradation, poor user experience
- **Mitigation Strategies**:
  - Comprehensive load testing dengan realistic traffic simulation
  - Layer 2 scaling solutions ready untuk deployment
  - Horizontal scaling architecture design dari awal
  - Performance monitoring dengan automatic alerting
  - Backup consensus mechanism options evaluated

**AI Algorithm Accuracy (Medium Risk)**
- **Description**: Machine learning recommendations yang tidak akurat dapat cause poor investment decisions
- **Impact**: Medium - Investor losses, platform credibility issues
- **Mitigation Strategies**:
  - Extensive training dataset dengan historical maritime data
  - Human oversight untuk high-value recommendations
  - Continuous model retraining dengan new data
  - A/B testing untuk algorithm improvements
  - Manual override capabilities untuk critical decisions

#### Business Risks

**Market Adoption Rate (Medium Risk)**
- **Description**: Slow adoption dari maritime industry stakeholders
- **Impact**: Medium - Delayed ROI, reduced platform value
- **Mitigation Strategies**:
  - Strategic partnerships dengan major maritime companies
  - Pilot programs dengan established players
  - Education dan awareness campaigns
  - Competitive pricing dan incentive structures
  - Gradual feature rollout dengan user feedback integration


#### Operational Risks

**Team Scalability (Medium Risk)**
- **Description**: Difficulty scaling technical team untuk meet development timelines
- **Impact**: Medium - Project delays, quality issues
- **Mitigation Strategies**:
  - Early identification of required skill sets
  - Multiple recruitment channels dan outsourcing options
  - Knowledge documentation untuk faster onboarding
  - Agile development practices untuk team flexibility
  - Backup resource plans dengan partner companies

**Third-party Dependencies (Low Risk)**
- **Description**: Failures dari external services like IPFS, cloud providers, APIs
- **Impact**: Low-Medium - Feature degradation, temporary service disruption
- **Mitigation Strategies**:
  - Multiple service providers untuk critical dependencies
  - Graceful degradation mechanisms
  - Regular health checks dan failover testing
  - Local caching dan backup systems
  - SLA agreements dengan penalty clauses

### Risk Monitoring Framework

#### Continuous Risk Assessment
- **Weekly Risk Reviews**: Team standup dengan risk identification
- **Monthly Stakeholder Reports**: Risk status updates dengan mitigation progress
- **Quarterly Risk Audits**: Comprehensive risk landscape evaluation
- **Annual Risk Strategy Review**: Risk management framework updates

#### Early Warning Systems
- **Technical Monitoring**: Automated alerting untuk performance degradation
- **Market Monitoring**: Industry news dan regulatory change tracking
- **User Feedback Monitoring**: Sentiment analysis dan usage pattern tracking
- **Financial Monitoring**: Budget tracking dan cost variance analysis

### Contingency Plans

#### Technical Contingencies
- **Blockchain Fallback**: Alternative consensus mechanisms ready
- **AI Failure Backup**: Manual review processes untuk critical decisions
- **Infrastructure Redundancy**: Multi-cloud deployment dengan failover capability
- **Security Breach Response**: Incident response plan dengan communication strategy

